message.content: It is difficult to make a generalization about the interests and obsessions of kids in Tajikistan, as each individual's preferences may vary. However, like in many other parts of the world, kids in Tajikistan might be interested in various things such as technology, social media, video games, sports, fashion, music, and popular culture. It is important to remember that the interests and obsessions of children can vary greatly, and not all kids will be obsessed with the same things.
